args: Wowzers! So this is a human castle, huh?
I'm glad you could make it, Fleur.
I can't believe I get to do a residency\nin a place like this.
Luca! Can you believe I'm here?\n'Cause I sure can't!
You're gonna love it. We got sylvans,\nwe got humans—we even got dragons!
It's the perfect spot to take your art\nto the next level.
Since the moment I got here, my creative\njuices have been RAGING. Like a river,\nyou know? Or a tiger!
Ha ha, I'm glad.\nWould you like a tour?
And this is going to be your room.
You're, uh, really into this, huh?
What do you mean?\n...Am I being weird?
Sorry, we just don't HAVE stuff like this\nin the forest. YOU know!
Heh, yeah, I know. This is all new\nto us sylvans.
The environment is perfect...\nThe people, inviting...\nI can't fail!
I'm gonna pioneer a new style of art,\nright here—one that perfectly blends\nsylvan and human influences!
What is it you want to paint, exactly?\nDo you have something in mind?
Course I do! It's...erm... A fusion of\ntwo cultures! And... Um...
Do you have a rough idea, at least?\nA tone, or maybe a color palette?
I... I did. But now that I'm really thinking\nabout it...maybe I didn't, actually.
My head is a total blank.\nAnd I guess my canvas is\ngonna stay that way too. Heh...
Give it some time; ya only just got here.
Look around—take in the sights\nand sounds and junk. I'm sure\nideas will start comin'.
Hey, I know—how bout I show ya\nsome of the stuff human culture\ninspired me to make?
Heh, I guess you could say that.\nCheck this out!
Uh... What am I looking at exactly?
This right here is my shocking syrup!
Shocking syrup! It's made by mixing spour\nfruit juice and human sweetener.
Adding it to food makes for some...\ninteresting results. Heh heh!
Ya wanna see? C'mon, let's head to\nthe kitchen.
It's fiiiine, nobody's gonna get hurt!\nBesides, Sarisse isn't even—
BWAH! Wh-what the heck are you\ndoin' here?!
I heard Fleur was around, so I came to\nsay hi. What are YOU up to, Luca?
Fleur, steer clear of this guy.\nAlso, hiiiiiiii!
'Cause all he does is prank people!
Every sylvan knows spour fruit is too\nsour to eat.
All his little syrup does is SLIGHTLY mask\nthe sourness with some sweetener.
At first your food is sweet, but suddenly\nyou're left with intense sourness.
Okay, so maybe it's a prank. I'm still using\na human invention to make an inedible\nfruit actually useful for once!
I dunno about you, but that sounds like\ncultural fusion to me.
See Fleur? It's just a prank.
What, no—c'mon, that's not the\nimportant part!
You invented something so amazing\nSarisse won't even let you USE it.
That's like, the DEFINITION of fantabulous.
Are you outta your—I mean, yeah! Totally!
Please let me study under you,\nMaster Luca!
M-master?! Hmmm... ＂Master＂... It's got a\npretty nice ring to it, actually.
Let me show ya some of my other\npra—er, artistic fusions. Heh heh.
A-actually, I just remembered Ranzal\nwanted to show me his new,\nuh...muscles! Yeah, can't miss that!
We can be master and pupil\nanother time, yeah? See ya!
There won't BE another time!\nGet BACK HEEEEERE!
Wow... What an artist...\nRanzal must be his muse.
Ha ha. Those two sure know how to\nwelcome someone.
I'm sure she'll be settled in no time.
And then, who knows what she'll end\nup creating?
